\[\mathcal{M}_{f}(\mathbf{x},\mathbf{y})=(\mu_{x}^{2}+\mu_{y}^{2}+c_{1})^{-1}(\sigma_{x} ^{2}+\sigma_{y}^{2}+c_{2})^{-1}(2\mu_{x}\mu_{y}+c_{1})(2\sigma_{x,y}+c_{2}).\]

